Description: desktop control panel for Cloudflare WARP
 WARP Control is a GTK desktop application for viewing connection state,
 managing split-tunnel exclusions, and customizing tray status colors.
 .
 Cloudflare WARP is installed separately and only after explicit confirmation;
 this package never adds a third-party repository during package installation.
